            <p part="N">Basileios kai Constantinos basileis Romaion.</p>
            <p xml:lang="en" part="N">Basil and Constantine, basileis of the Romans.</p>
            <p xml:lang="fr" part="N">Basile et Constantin, basileis des Romains.</p>
